  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to employ the supplement L-arginine to test the hypothesis that
      activation of blood flow to the brain during cognitive tasks is regulated by nitric oxide in
      older subjects with diabetes mellitus and/or hypertension (high blood pressure).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
